[gd_scene load_steps=16 format=3]

; Dev-only greybox for the task-04 manual playtest (F6). Not wired into GameManager —
; mission flow is task 11. A stationary DetectionSensor faces the player spawn with a
; debug cone (green→yellow→orange→red). Walk into the cone to fill it; duck behind the
; CoverWall to break LoS and recover; step into the ShadowZone to slow detection; make
; noise (sprint) to flip it Suspicious toward you. Positions are tunable.

